snippet.title: Evernight - The Reign of Darkness
snippet.description:
Evernight is a Turn Based Massively Multiplayer Online Role Playing Game. Use strategy and diplomacy skills to conquer foes and dominate the world. Combines the strategic elements of Risk and Chess with Role-playing and Fantasy elements to create an unrivaled online community.
http://www.evernightgame.com/index.asp
